    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Anno ab incarnacione millesimo
                        cemtesimo hoctavo, temporibus dominus <persName key="#Popes"
                            ref="#people/4303">Pascasius</persName> pape, Henricus inperator
                        defuntus est anno secundo, die quarto decimo mensis decembris, indictione
                        secunda, <placeName ref="#places/4179">Pumposie</placeName>. Petistis a me
                        in Dei nomine <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Rusticus Pomposianus"
                                >Rusticus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Levies #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in Pumposa</orgName>, per
                        uxionem domini <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/4306"
                            >Liutofredi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> suprascripti monasterii, tibi presenti in
                        Christi nomine <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Petrus de Marotia"
                                >Petrus de Marocia </name></persName> petitore pro te et pro
                            <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Aemilia"
                            >Imilla</name></persName> iugale tue seu pro filiis vestris masculi − et
                        si filium masculo non abetis cadat in femine − <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libell(um) nomine </rs> concedistis
                        nobis, idest tota et integra omnes res quantascumque vos petitoris abetis
                        per interiore libellum de iuris predicto monasterio in <rs
                            key="#Fundi"
                            >fundo</rs> qui vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Levies"
                                ><placeName
                                    key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Levies"
                                    >Canitulo</placeName></geogName> et in <placeName
                                        key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Fundi #Landed_possessions #Penalty #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Wine #Linen #Pigs #Sheep #Poultry #Exenia #Levies"
                                        >Paturiano</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs> et <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs> et cum omnibus sibi
                        pertinentibus; abendum, tenendum, possidendum, supersedendum et in omnibus
                        meliorandum in anni viginti et novem ad renovandum. Sub <rs key="#Levies"
                            >teraticum</rs> de omni <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">labore maiore</rs>
                        septimo, <rs key="#Linen">lino</rs> similiter, <rs key="#Cereals #Minores"
                            >minuto</rs> hoctavo, <rs key="#Wine">vino</rs> tertjo, arbore pecto
                        ponente semel, <rs key="#Exenia">exenio</rs> de grano stario uno et <rs
                            key="#Poultry">pullo</rs> uno, pro ipsa tollere debatis <rs key="#Size"
                            >una tornaturia</rs> pro <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">orto </rs> et area
                        et atego et omnique anno pro <rs key="#Pigs">porco</rs> et <rs key="#Sheep"
                            >angno</rs> solidos trex denariorum Venecie, in nativitas Domini spalla
                        una de porco et fogacie due et in sancti Apolinari pulli dui et fogacie due
                        et in vendimie pullo uno et fogacia una et omni domada opera una a manibus,
                        aducto ipsum retditum per vos <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">colonis</rs> usque
                        in <rs key="#Cities">tjvitate</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/594">Ravene</placeName>, in domo
                        nostro Sancti Stefani cum fide et puritate; callciario solidorum
                        quadragimta. Autoriare et defensare prom(ittimus), sub pene <rs
                            key="#Penalty">auri untja una</rs> et post pene solut(ionem) m(aneat)
                        peticionis in sua firmitate. Quem vero paginam <persName key="#Tabellio"
                                ><name ref="Gherardus">Gerardum</name>
                        </persName> in Dei nomine <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellionem</rs> de civitate
                            <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/3515">Liviensi</placeName>
                        scrib(en)d(am) rogavi, sub die et mense, indictione suprascripta secunda. +
                        Singnum + + + manus Petrus ad omnia predicta.</ab>
